**** Important ideas
- Three ways to become successful:

  - Be savvy with the most valuable tools, which in our current world, is either AI or computers. 
  - Be the best at what you do, like acting, singing, writing, or software engineering
  - Have a lot of capital to invest in the hottest things, like being a VC firm investing in instagram in its early stages.

- As you learn a new skill, Myelin, a layer of fatty tissue that grows around neurons, develop around the relevant neurons and allow them to fire more effortlessly and effctively.
- High-quality work produced = (Time Spent) X (Intensity of Focus)
- When you are multi-tasking, as you switch from task A to task B, a residue of your attention remains stuck thinking about the original task. This makes you more likely to perform poorly on your next task.

